; fn_main_pseudo_3d_map_render_pipeline
;
; Main pseudo-3D map render pipeline: build visible-cell staging stream,
; dispatch cell draw paths, then blit viewport strips to ZX bitmap.
;
; .
;
; Args: none.
; .
; Returns: none.
; .
