; 0xA8C4/0xA8C5; move delta 0xA8C6; frame timer pair 0xA8CD/0xA8CE; directional
; pointers 0xA8CF..0xA8D6; mask 0xA8D7; progress bytes 0xA8D8..0xA8DA.
