; fn_hud_bar_updater
;
; HUD bar updater: adjust one vertical meter row at HL using current value A
; and previous value C.
;
; .
;
; Args: HL_bar is ptr_u8 meter-row base; A_new is u8 new value; C_old is u8
; previous value; B_fill is u8 marker byte.
; .
